tips.text: Their speciality here is their roast duck and my favourite would be the Dang Gui flavour!
Pancakes with the most awesome maple butter! And thick milkshakes.
They put way too much fake cheese on my eggs, ruined the meal. Service was good and the whole place is very cute and unique, expensive tho. Smoked salmon+dessert+service charge= 40SGD
Delicious ... Must try!
Excellent local flavored teochew porridge.  Great value buffet. Loved the braised meat, curry chicken, Ma la tofu and also the black carrot cake. Had a great time with family. Will be back!!
Same group as the Teppei @ Orchid hotel that is dam difficult to get in. Must try the chunky sashimi chirashi Don. bring your own wasabi if you dun wana pay $0.50 for needing more :( #ThomtoriEats
Good pizzas at reasonable prices. Choose you own sauce, cheese & toppings with the DIY option; fun with interesting options like blue crab & roasted squash but nothing special.
Super affordable! and great wine collection too
Try the crayfish:)

tips.text: Loves the cheese creamy bun!
Love the beer selection  here! They have more than 30 beers of different flavours for selection. Beer, paired with their skewers 🍢!
One of our followers recommend the cutlets! Try and let us know if you love it!
The Singapore Slings here are better than at Raffles and the wifi is wicked fast. You can cut your dining budget by visiting during Evening Cocktails. The space is lovely.
Nice mixed tandoori platter
The carrot cake here sucks. Pls don't eat!!! Hokkien Mee and Oyster omelette sucks. Even the sugar cane tastes diluted
It's the only churros outfit here that does churros with cream fillings. The cream cheese churros was pretty unique, and the dark chocolate-coated churros hold up better if you're taking them away.
Omega 3 Baby! is fantabulous!
Wonderful place for lunch or dinner. Great, fresh produce. Chef/owner wants you to eat well! Very affordable. Hearty salads for $8.
Friendly and helpful staff. Quality of the meat is awesome! Had the Fuku set, great value.
i still want some more of the  black pepper crab.....
Free wifi: 55W password: Godbless
Must bring your family here... The food is high standard,  They have private function room too... Worth the money!!! You will never regret!!!
Excellent food and you would expect no less when you find out that the former Chef from Taste Paradise is helming the kitchen.
One of the few sandwich places that offers a variety of vegetarian options that is not just made out of cheese. Grilled veggie chutney is very filling. A bit bland but it's healthy. Not complaining.
Here for Sunday brunch and left unimpressed with the food. Basilico's brunch is much better. But u do get a good view with nice interiors. Service is also earnest.
The gnochhi is light and still has a nice texture - wine selection is small but good - try the truffle raviolis.
Service here during weekday lunch is horrible! Probably due I lack of staff.

Any of the burgers are great, washed down with a Brewdog IPA
